{"tid":2036954,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"成個手袋唔見左 好驚","createTime":"2020-05-26T18:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T07:24:22.000Z","uid":359314,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa906e42281255f48609ce68acca16098471a72b","tid":2036954,"uid":359314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:14:05.000Z","msg":"話說係17號夜晚因為自己大頭蝦啲嘢出晒嚟 係維園唔見左個自己儲左好耐辛苦錢買換來ge手袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  心痛還心痛  但呢幾日我個心都囉囉攣 係因為入面幾乎有曬我所有資料 身分證 銀行卡 學生證 回鄉證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜x證都係曬入邊  好驚個人會拎我身分證or回鄉證走去借財仔之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當日搞左一大輪 我報左警 但今日先至收到張警處寄黎屋企report/lose poverty 確認信之類 發現上面有列明個袋入面有d咩物品 但冇寫到有身分證同回鄉證兩個最可能令到我賴嘢嘅兩張證  我心諗係咪嗰時太心急唔記得咗講入邊仲有我身分證and 回鄉證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  身分證係已經唔見兩日後先book到補領 回鄉證依家就冇報失都冇申請補領 但我依家好驚個仆街賊會用到我身分證借財仔 or用回鄉證上大陸借錢之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇人可以比少少建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚"},{"pid":"1137d52d77dfebbbe0a93251c444be56999fd6b4","tid":2036954,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"講故台"},{"pid":"db59fdf8b787c5fc587beae9cd5aab5fa718019a","tid":2036954,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"開錯台"},{"pid":"b9b5e5193c0ca01f856130c88df6975f7c553f47","tid":2036954,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:46:42.000Z","msg":"備定案先囉"},{"pid":"d9dd3a17a2801597205c5a077dc0419f29251e62","tid":2036954,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:51:05.000Z","msg":"孭孭下個手袋都可以唔見？"},{"pid":"378029edf5367b124f3925da8b5e918506bccad2","tid":2036954,"uid":359314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9dd3a17a2801597205c5a077dc0419f29251e62","tid":2036954,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:51:05.000Z","msg":"孭孭下個手袋都可以唔見？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:45:14.000Z","msg":"喺張凳度坐左陣將個袋擺喺隔離 起程嘅時候唔記得拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273b4f04e6ca832c7fc2ecc29283cc29a12ed284","tid":2036954,"uid":359314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9b5e5193c0ca01f856130c88df6975f7c553f47","tid":2036954,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:46:42.000Z","msg":"備定案先囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"當日已經備左案  但唔知佢哋知唔知我身分證同回鄉證都唔見埋"},{"pid":"f3e5779511a70e51568813e0a506153cefd1fe78","tid":2036954,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"273b4f04e6ca832c7fc2ecc29283cc29a12ed284","tid":2036954,"uid":359314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9b5e5193c0ca01f856130c88df6975f7c553f47","tid":2036954,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:46:42.000Z","msg":"備定案先囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"當日已經備左案  但唔知佢哋知唔知我身分證同回鄉證都唔見埋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"咁你備案果時緊係要講埋呢樣 起碼有d證明 你呢個期間無用證件做過d咩丫嗎......"},{"pid":"8549ae8f1326f19386628f4f4f190d61da7a9aef","tid":2036954,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"樓主做女朋友既話，個男仔應該好慘"},{"pid":"fca8c6a6b404ab906dbbb905cc13b0543f4fa6cf","tid":2036954,"uid":359314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f3e5779511a70e51568813e0a506153cefd1fe78","tid":2036954,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"273b4f04e6ca832c7fc2ecc29283cc29a12ed284","tid":2036